Ladies and gentlemen,</i>

21
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:22,090
<i>we are about to begin our
descent into Phuket Airport.</i>

22
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:24,043
<i>The local time is 1:30 in the afternoon...</i>

23
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,525
