MAN: Have you been to Khao Lak before?

44
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,160
HENRY: No, it's our first time.

45
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,487
MAN: This is the best holiday season ever.

46
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:43,689
All resorts are full,
