50
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,367
All right.

51
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:53,489
MARIA: I'm sorry, but we made
a booking on the third floor.

52
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,686
The Sea View Room.

53
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:56,967
