00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,041
THOMAS: No, it's not.

86
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:10,527
It's going a different way than the others.

87
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,722
It's going all the way up now.

88
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,120
- It's catching up!
- Yeah, it's catching up.

