107
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,881
The money's going outside!

108
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,961
MARIA: No, no, no!

109
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,805
Wait, wait! One at a time!

110
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,804
