831
01:18:32,595 --> 01:18:34,836
We are doing the best we can.

832
01:18:34,915 --> 01:18:37,759
We are taking your mom
to surgery right away.

833
01:18:52,195 --> 01:18:53,765
(SPEAKING THAI)

