850
01:19:44,955 --> 01:19:46,320
(WEAKLY) Lucas.

851
01:19:47,995 --> 01:19:49,485
Lucas.

852
01:19:51,755 --> 01:19:54,361
Anything left in the can?

853
01:20:00,315 --> 01:20:02,966
