Dad!

856
01:22:26,675 --> 01:22:27,915
Dad!

857
01:22:29,955 --> 01:22:31,081
Dad!

858
01:22:36,675 --> 01:22:37,801
Dad!

859
01:23:08,035 --> 01:23:09,275
