993
01:36:50,595 --> 01:36:52,199
I'll see you once you get there.

994
01:36:52,275 --> 01:36:53,640
Have a safe flight.

995
01:37:31,755 --> 01:37:32,756
Okay.

996
01:37:36,755 --> 01:37:38,200
